OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,FA woman in Birmingham has reportedly
OL,8,Foffered #100 to remove rubbish she
OL,9,Fclaims was "dumped" in her back garden.
OL,11,FThe woman by the name "Chanel C",
OL,12,Foffered the work to someone on the
OL,13,Fwebsite Airtasker, which allows people
OL,14,Fto outsource work for everyday tasks.
OL,16,FThe woman said black bags full of
OL,17,Frubbish had been left at her address,
OL,18,Fand that she needed them removed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,FShe set a price of #100 for the work,
OL,8,Fand a number of people have replied
OL,9,Foffering to assist.
OL,11,FElsewhere in the city, one person
OL,12,Foffered #90 for rubbish removal and
OL,13,Fanother offered #30, for around 18
OL,14,Fblack bin bags of general rubbish.
OL,16,FThe bin strike dispute is now in its
OL,17,Fsecond year, following months of
OL,18,Fdisruption to waste collection
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,FLast month Cllr John Cotton, the
OL,8,FLeader of Labour-run Birmingham City
OL,9,FCouncil, said a "negotiated settlement
OL,10,Fto end the bin strike is now within
OL,11,Fsight".
OL,13,FBut he made clear in his statement the
OL,14,Fpre-election period stops the council
OL,15,Ffrom making a final decision prior to
OL,16,Fthe day of the local elections, on the
OL,17,F7th May.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,FThis was met with scepticism and anger
OL,8,Ffrom opposition councillors, and Unite
OL,9,Fthe Union says there will now be a
OL,10,Fseries of meetings to complete the
OL,11,Foffer.
OL,13,FIt has warned that if the deal is
OL,14,Freneged on in any way, the dispute
OL,15,Fwill be escalated.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
