PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,FWest Midlands Mayor Richard Parker has
OL,8,Fcriticised Birmingham City Council
OL,9,Fofficials, accusing them of slowing
OL,10,Fefforts to end the long-running bin
OL,11,Fstrike.
OL,13,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,14,FCentral, Labour's Parker said the
OL,15,Fprocess had been undermined by
OL,16,F"frustration, obfuscation and delay".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
