PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778091067
OL,3,CBirmingham resident offers #100 to
OL,4,Cremove 'dumped' rubbish as bin strike
OL,5,Cgoes on
OL,7,F"My message to those still taking
OL,8,Findustrial action is simple: come back
OL,9,Fto work as I want you to be part of
OL,10,Fthis new and improved service. Our
OL,11,Fdoor remains open."
